5:41"},{"id":"01998e3a-3406-73f9-8874-03046e38c7af","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5624,"content":"打个12345问问很难吗？话费都充不起为什么不回老家啃馒头","createdAt":"2025-09-28T10:50:03"},{"id":"01998e4e-25cc-704c-94d6-a681d5de2776","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23274,"content":"据我观察，房子没买的，买车大概率也不考虑电车，平时也不舍得油费和车位费，更愿意骑电动车上班","createdAt":"2025-09-28T11:11:50"},{"id":"01998e54-da59-71cd-a37f-b1f392de7568","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2921,"content":"所以那帮狗比开始出租房税了，谁也跑不了","createdAt":"2025-09-28T11:19:09"},{"id":"01998e5c-129c-737c-ad11-c442200dcb5b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":26811,"content":"不结婚就对不起父母吗？大清都亡了","createdAt":"2025-09-28T11:27:02"},{"id":"01998ece-e91a-7194-9ff6-e3936e9244f2","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21818,"content":"18、19年真是俩眼一抹黑，脑瓜嗡嗡的","createdAt":"2025-09-28T13:32:28"},{"id":"01998ed3-02c8-71ca-856c-305cedf5b038","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":23223,"content":"掏空父母钱包，让父母给你带娃，就对得起父母了？那祝您多子多福，房子买十套！","createdAt":"2025-09-28T13:36:57"},{"id":"01998ef6-72eb-720f-ba7a-b8bc4fdab496","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7344,"content":"还爱吃超意兴","createdAt":"2025-09-28T14:15:40"},{"id":"01998f0c-eb2d-72f0-b5aa-70629842cdc2","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24061,"content":"对，你这个可以","createdAt":"2025-09-28T14:40:12"},{"id":"01999387-3df9-7351-b779-ab17f3eac65f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":27118,"content":"人必须接受掌控不了自己的命运，自以为努力，以为看得清，其实活在圈养的圈子里，天界之人以我族天骄为食","createdAt":"2025-09-29T11:32:18"},{"id":"0199982b-196f-734f-803e-94c4a3dbf98f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5689,"content":"我不是2015年买的，是2015年有这想法，真正买房是在2024年。","createdAt":"2025-09-30T09:09:45"}]